<item>
            <title>[SUREFIRE-376] TestNG @AfterSuite failures are ignored</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-376</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Run the attached test, which includes a TestNG test like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;public class TestNGSuiteTest {&lt;br/&gt;
	@Test public void doNothing() {}&lt;br/&gt;
	@AfterSuite public void failAfterSuite() &lt;/p&gt;
{ Assert.fail(); }
&lt;p&gt;}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When you run &quot;mvn test&quot;, the test will pass, but it should fail.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
